energy bar
- gradient in middle
- pieces use rect

buttons ui
- cancel target_loc button
- shift click selects all in between
- ctrl click multi select
- click unselects everything else

animations, prev pos, curr pos
- progress = move_timer / move_cd * 2

remake mechanics
- unit class
	- 2 hp calvary, fast
	- 3 hp defender, high atk very slow
	- 5 hp = power house (energy regen++), cannot move, spawn point
	- 10 hp = radar, deploy everywhere
